# Blog Project Rules

This is a Hugo blog. See CLAUDE.md for full documentation.

## Key Workflow: Syncing WeChat Articles

When the user says they published a new WeChat article, run:

```bash
node sync-wechat.js <article_url>
```

This handles everything: fetch, parse, categorize, dedup, and write to `content/zh/posts/`.

## Project Structure

- `content/zh/posts/{category}/` — Chinese posts organized by category
- `content/en/` — English translations
- `sync-wechat.js` — WeChat article sync script
- `autoTranslate.js` — AI translation script
- `hugo.toml` — Hugo config
- `.sync-history.json` — Tracks synced articles for dedup
